snippet.title: InfidHells - Devlog 01
snippet.description:
Here is my new project InfidHells !
It is weird for me to go back on Youtube with a personal project...
It's not some Dark Souls shitpost I'm afraid... This period of my life is now over (for now at least, we never know ^^).
